Description:
Bordering the cliff you see a man with the appearance of a merchant running in a hurry.

A few meters from him a patrol of goblin raiders is chasing him and will catch him shortly.

If you wish to intervene, you can attempt a quick ambush, but failing may result in the merchant being killed before you can react.
DescriptionAction: Do you want to help the merchant?
